      <h2>What We Build</h2>

      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Northway Construction specializes in commercial construction across multiple sectors. Our portfolio includes office buildings and corporate spaces, religious and educational facilities, historical restoration projects, government and military facilities, and tenant improvements and build-outs. We handle projects ranging from small renovations to major ground-up construction—providing quality craftsmanship and personal service on every project.</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h3>Service Areas</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">We serve commercial construction clients throughout Utah from our Eagle Mountain office, with particular strength in Salt Lake City, Provo-Orem, Park City, Lehi, American Fork, Payson, Bluffdale, Utah County, Salt Lake County, and all along the Wasatch Front.</p>
      </div>
